{"tid":2518470,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"二手速遞｜迎海．星灣御兩房減60萬沽 6年升值不足百萬","createTime":"2021-05-06T04:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T05:08:27.000Z","uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd9b63e6da1d6f4aa95dfc8511806796d01cbe3","tid":2518470,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T04:58:27.000Z","msg":"二手速遞｜迎海．星灣御兩房減60萬沽 6年升值不足百萬 AM730 May 6 2021 - 07:42<br />\n<br />\n二手交投向好，個別業主調整叫價吸引買家。世紀21奇豐物業雲海分行高級分行經理蔡蓓表示，馬鞍山迎海．星灣御17座高層E室，實用面積約498方呎，兩房兩廳間隔，座向西面望園景。原叫價940萬元，放盤1個月，減價60萬元或約6.4%，以880萬元沽出，實用面積呎價約17,671元。<br />\n據了解，原業主於2015年7月購入上址，當時作價782萬元，持貨近6年至今沽售，帳面獲利98萬元，單位期內升值約13%。<br />\n<br />\n「文章版權為新傳媒集團所擁有，原文請按： <a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/276297/?utm_campaign=copy」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2F276297%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dcopy%E3%80%8D&d=lnSleIYCVJUMUgC9CFuHQi2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=e655d964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/276297/?utm_campaign=copy」</a>"},{"pid":"1265579b9c27c009d76ee83906cd800044d9f46d","tid":2518470,"uid":49830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"mos交通咁垃圾，有升仲想點"},{"pid":"0f47351c63fd41b796adad4a639605ccabbcf282","tid":2518470,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"880萬..."},{"pid":"2767ef3ba4d6ca334adea39995232b51bd3f427c","tid":2518470,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1265579b9c27c009d76ee83906cd800044d9f46d","tid":2518470,"uid":49830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"mos交通咁垃圾，有升仲想點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T05:08:27.000Z","msg":"迎海由第一期4XX萬2房爆升上黎都幾勁"}]}